  "prompt": "How do I rent a two wheeler in Mumbai?",
  "response": "Renting a two-wheeler in Mumbai is a convenient option for locals and tourists alike. Here\u2019s a step-by-step guide on how to do it:\n\n---\n\n### 1. **Choose a Rental Service Provider**\n   - **Online Platforms**: Use popular rental apps and websites like:\n     - **Royal Brothers**\n     - **Zoomcar** (for bikes)\n     - **ONN Bikes**\n     - **RentOnGo**\n     - **Vogo** (for scooters)\n   - **Local Rentals**: You can also find local bike rental shops in areas like Colaba, Andheri, or Bandra.\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Check Eligibility**\n   - **Age**: Usually, you must be at least 18/21 years old.\n   - **Driving License**: A valid Indian or international driving license is mandatory.\n   - **ID Proof**: Carry an Aadhar card, PAN card, or passport for verification.\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Book the Two-Wheeler**\n   - **Online Booking**:\n     - Download the app or visit the website of your chosen rental provider.\n     - Select the two-wheeler model (scooter, bike, etc.).\n     - Choose the rental duration (hourly, daily, or weekly).\n     - Pay the deposit and booking fee online.\n   - **Offline Booking**: Visit a local rental shop, submit your documents, and book the vehicle.\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Pick Up the Vehicle**\n   - Collect the two-wheeler from the designated location.\n   - Verify the vehicle\u2019s condition (e.g., scratches, fuel level) and ensure you receive a rental agreement.\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Safety and Guidelines**\n   - Wear a helmet (often provided by the rental service).\n   - Follow traffic rules and wear masks if required.\n   - Avoid overloading the vehicle.\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Return the Vehicle**\n   - Return the bike to the agreed location on time.\n   - Ensure it\u2019s in the same condition as when you picked it up.\n   - The deposit will be refunded after inspection (minus any damages or penalties).\n\n---\n\n### Tips:\n   - Compare prices across platforms to get the best deal.\n   - Read reviews and check the rental provider\u2019s reputation.\n   - Inspect the bike thoroughly before taking it to avoid disputes later.\n\nEnjoy exploring Mumbai on two wheels! \ud83c\udfcd\ufe0f",
